name: Breakfast Replay
description:
It was 05.30 am, Lola still comfortably snuggle inside her blanket. Birds are chirping happily outside 

" I better get up before the sun getting higher, let's conquer that 5k" 

Quickly she jumped from the bed and play her fav beat, she opened her coffee can 

"no coffee?.. ah okay some crackers and a glass of milk will do!" 

While having her simple breakfast, Lola look up for today's weather forecast, it's gonna be cloudy today but no rain and that's good! 

After she took her 5k run, the hood was having a garage sale bazaar, think she might hang out a little while, maybe she'll pick up a few things she might like. Lola smiled when she found this box full of old records. So she go home carrying some records she just bought, a cup of coffe and a bowl of warm chicken porridge... and some fried dumplings. What an awesome morning! Her morning was kindly rewarding. "Now let's eat! and enjoy the rest of the day" 


00:35 secs 1080x1080p
animated drawings + instrumental beat.
